{
  "page": "Grazdan (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The first name <b>Grazdan</b> is a popular name among the <a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari\" title=\"Ghiscari\">Ghiscari</a> and can refer to any of the following characters:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_the_Great\" title=\"Grazdan the Great\">Grazdan the Great</a>, the legendary founder of Old Ghis</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_(tall_one)\" title=\"Grazdan (tall one)\">Grazdan</a>, a Good Master of Astapor, a tall man</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_(fat_one)\" title=\"Grazdan (fat one)\">Grazdan</a>, a Good Master of Astapor, a fat man</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_(spiked_beard)\" title=\"Grazdan (spiked beard)\">Grazdan</a>, a Good Master of Astapor, a man with a spiked beard</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_mo_Ullhor\" title=\"Grazdan mo Ullhor\">Grazdan mo Ullhor</a>, a Good Master of Astapor</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_mo_Eraz\" title=\"Grazdan mo Eraz\">Grazdan mo Eraz</a>, a Wise Master of Yunkai</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_zo_Galare\" title=\"Grazdan zo Galare\">Grazdan zo Galare</a>, a former slave merchant of Meereen</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grazdan_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Grazdhan_zo_Rhaezn\" title=\"Grazdhan zo Rhaezn\">Grazdhan zo Rhaezn</a>, a Yunkish nobleman</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grazhar_zo_Galare\" title=\"Grazhar zo Galare\">Grazhar zo Galare</a>, a child of a Meereenese slaving family, erroneously called \"Grazdar\" on two occasions.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403154945\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: fals